  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0db4\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Peradeniya University student dies after falling from Saradiel rock",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mawanella Police say that a student of Peradeniya University who came to see Saradiyal Rock in Mawanella Uthuankanda fell from the rock and died due to serious injuries.",
        "A 27-year-old youth from Elpitiya has died in this incident. Almost 60 students, including her, have come to see the Saradial rock this morning by passenger buses from Peradeniya.",
        "Later, he climbed the mountain from Uthuankande to visit the Saradial Rock and the accident must have happened at the top of the mountain, said Mawanella Police Station Chief Inspector Lasantha Kaluarachichi.",
        "He further said that this student has completed her graduation but she is still pursuing further education in the same university",
        "is engaged in He said that during that time, Saradial might have visited here to see the rock and for some studies there.",
        "The body has been deposited at the Mawanella General Hospital and the Mawanella Police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
